				<p>After several weeks of hearing from the community, we&#8217;re happy to announce new pricing for ExpressionEngine 7.</p>

<h2>New Pricing</h2>

<ul>
<li><strong>Core</strong> - We&#8217;re keeping the Core of ExpressionEngine 7 free! </li>
<li><strong>Pro</strong> - Pro opens up unlimited control panel users and is initially $249 for the 1st year of updates. After your first year, a Pro license can be renewed for as low as $49/yr.</li>
<li><strong>MSM</strong> - Each additional MSM site license is $49 for the 1st year of updates, and can then be renewed for as low as $39/year.</li>
</ul>

<p class="text-center"><a href="/store/purchase-pro" class="bg-red text-white mt-6 inline-block px-8 border border-red border-solid rounded-md text-center text-base font-normal lg:mt-6 leading-50 hover:bg-white hover:text-red " style="color:#fff;">Purchase ExpressionEngine Pro</a></p>

<h2>What&#8217;s Changed</h2>

<h3>User Limits</h3>

<p>Originally we released ExpressionEngine 7 with all of the <a href="/features">new features</a> as well as <a href="/introducing-expressionengine-pro">all the features</a> that were previously only available with a Pro license for Free when a site only needs 1 registered user. If you needed more users (with Control Panel access or without), you needed to purchase a Pro license. We&#8217;ve updated this to now allow <strong>unlimited non-control panel users</strong> in the Core version for free. This allows for more freedom on sites that only need 1 user with Control Panel access, but still want to allow users to register to leave comments, create e-commerce accounts, update content via Channel Forms, or other member functions. If you need more than one user with Control Panel access, a Pro license will still be required.</p>

<h3>Pricing</h3>

<p>Initially, a Pro license for ExpressionEngine 7 was going to remain the same as it had been for ExpressionEngine 6: $199/yr. Our goal is to build ExpressionEngine as a stable platform that everyone can thrive off of. However, it was clear from the community that the current pricing just was missing the mark. In light of this, <strong>we have updated the pricing for ExpressionEngine Pro to $249</strong> for the 1st year of updates. After your first year, a Pro license can be renewed for $49/yr when you subscribe to yearly renewals or $59 for a single year of updates.</p>

<p><strong>MSM licenses have also been reduced</strong> from $99/yr to $49 for the 1st year of updates, and can then be renewed for $39/year when you subscribe to yearly renewals or $49 for a single year of updates.</p>

<h3>Pro With ExpressionEngine 6</h3>

<p>If you need to purchase a Pro license for use with ExpressionEngine 6, these licenses have also been reduced to the above pricing. If you are currently using Pro with ExpressionEngine 6, <strong>your yearly renewal will be reduced to $49/yr</strong>.</p>

<h2>Pro License Discounts</h2>

<p class="text-purple-lighter font-bold leading-none" style="font-size: 3.75rem;margin-bottom: 10px;"><strike class="font-light opacity-40 text-4xl">$249</strike>$189</p>

<p><strong>For the next two weeks (Aug 24 - Sept 7) a Single Site Pro license is on sale for only $189!</strong> No limit on licenses purchased during this sale.</p>

<p class="text-center"><a href="/store/purchase-pro" class="bg-red text-white mt-6 inline-block px-8 border border-red border-solid rounded-md text-center text-base font-normal lg:mt-6 leading-50 hover:bg-white hover:text-red " style="color:#fff;">Purchase ExpressionEngine Pro</a></p>

